0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"帶風向玩輿論可以撚到班無批判性思考既傻仔唔想反抗，easy <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0122db574f75e0ba50fd1b5f0ecb411eaf32870","tid":2089303,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1d5e4c4bde603f2981d16fc6aa138346f3258d5","tid":2089303,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:34:12.000Z","msg":"BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。"},{"pid":"91acaf0d0013ebd827305a93447bd064f35cd959","tid":2089303,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7deb6df98662a56837c50058240c531ac160ab4","tid":2089303,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32c5b6d98c0e36453629626990bbb1540d9d667","tid":2089303,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:37:47.000Z","msg":"係連登有bno一定唔走<br />\n話走就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fc5570780dcdc05a333c463f6c0727e5422462","tid":2089303,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"294b7b2470564cebf08e68e8ebb1c38685ce5416","tid":2089303,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10b74afcb87a0a5a3c572dba6d5ebc72f31c046","tid":2089303,"uid":347944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7477993bcc81beee7a82e6bcadd1497cebd283de","tid":2089303,"uid":357421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"一句五毛國安分化撚就當應咗啲質問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed44ec77264a4777e931ca0de2ba4d770ecfb6d3","tid":2089303,"uid":361753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:01:24.00